<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Lienrum</author>
<hymn_number>246</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel Aigupta gam ahin,
 Muonna kipahna ka hawla;
 Damsung mat zawh guon ka bawla,
 Kahna leh lungkhamna mai a hung hii.

[V2]
 Aw, ka pienna hi kumsawt gam ei puoi,
 Muonna kipahna hawl mah leng
 Mu zo puong ie, a mun ei puoi,
 Lal Krista gam ahih loh ziekin.

[V3]
 2. Gam beimang dinga lenghaw hi,
 Ei tatna thisan lun ziekin;
 Kumsawta hinna chang dingin,
 Namtin chitin a dingin A hawng tai.

[V4]
 3. Aw zie muna chun leng dingin,
 Lalpa, Na hatnan ei puiin,
 Khawvel nunnawp beimanna hi,
 Ngaiin en nawn puong ie nunlui gam hi.

[V5]
 4. Hehpihna Lal gam zuon dingin,
 Aw ka lautha nang le hawlin;
 Khawvel hawihnan hun sam mah leh,
 Lili pak Lal nunnem in A hun ngak.</lyrics>
<title>Khawvel Aigupta</title>
</song>